sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant A as External Agent
    participant MW as ProjectTokenMiddleware
    participant M as MCP Tool Handler
    participant C as Query Cache
    participant G as GraphRegistry and FalkorDB
    participant P as MCPProducer
    participant Q as Redis Jobs Stream
    participant I as IndexerConsumer
    participant Admin as Admin API

    A->>MW: Call ContextGraph MCP tool
    alt Token missing or revoked
        MW-->>A: Reject request with 401 or 403
    else Token accepted
        MW->>M: Continue request in project scope
        opt Cache unavailable
            M->>C: Attempt cache read
            C-->>M: Cache error
            Note over M,C: Tool continues without cache
        end

        alt Graph retrieval is weak or incomplete
            M->>G: Query graph anyway
            G-->>M: Sparse result set
            Note over M,A: CG-first strategy falls back to bounded local snippets
            M-->>A: Partial graph evidence plus local fallback
        else Graph retrieval is healthy
            M-->>A: Graph-backed answer
        end
    end

    A->>M: Request index_repo_changes
    alt Deleted or renamed files detected
        Note over M,P: Tool escalates to full index because incremental does not purge stale symbols
        M->>P: Enqueue full index job
    else Safe incremental change set
        M->>P: Enqueue incremental index job
    end

    P->>Q: Publish job
    I->>Q: Consume job
    alt Pipeline failure while processing
        Note over I,Q: Job marked failed and stream entry is not ACKed
        I-->>Admin: Failed job visible in index status
    else Worker stalls on processing
        Admin->>I: Recover stale jobs by repo
        I->>Q: ACK stale stream entry during recovery
        I-->>Admin: Job marked failed for manual retry
    else Pipeline succeeds
        I->>Q: ACK message
        I-->>Admin: Job status becomes done
    end